headline: Here are the Factors Impacting Zebra Technologies’ (ZBRA)
summary: RS Investments, an investment management company, released its “RS Large Cap Value Strategy” first quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the first quarter, the strategy underperformed its benchmark, the Russell 1000 Value Index (the “Index”), and returned 1.57% (net) versus a return of 2.14% for the Index. […]
